{"tid":2164763,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（估國家） 女學生急救途中被救護車直送殯儀館","createTime":"2020-08-19T11:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T12:41:22.000Z","uid":222970,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2ad1764310d4768fa7b80c55c8961d0a8ee7abdf","tid":2164763,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T11:19:57.000Z","msg":"【女學生急救途中被救護車直送殯儀館】<br />\n<br />\n六月中江蘇鹽城一個中三女學生，在課室突然暈倒，校方隨即送她到衛生院，同時叫救護車。<br />\n<br />\n女生母親說，急救員趕到衛生院時，指該女生已沒有生命跡象，但在衛生院勸喻下，答應送女生到縣人民醫院搶救，但救護車直接開到殯儀館，跟車的老師投訴，而且殯儀館基於沒有醫院死亡證拒收後，再把女生送到醫院搶救，最終女生死亡。<br />\n<br />\n官方回應指是安撫家屬，才把女生抬上救護車，做法合規。<br />\n<br />\n#送院變送殯儀館<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MyMNFv0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMyMNFv0.jpg&h=21be5f2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6475c1a46fabdd4bd4d96f1eb4051964ebbdc787","tid":2164763,"uid":222970,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T11:20:54.000Z","msg":"地獄鬼國嘅潛規則：就係要封利是比救護員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe0fe8b59b29df603b173f2059412a1cd8298ac","tid":2164763,"uid":18999,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T11:21:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7sDgy3s.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7sDgy3s.gif&h=80fc00ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a23fdabcfde5989271a8ea2a3b55cfd29076a627","tid":2164763,"uid":171074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fbe0fe8b59b29df603b173f2059412a1cd8298ac","tid":2164763,"uid":18999,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T11:21:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7sDgy3s.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7sDgy3s.gif&h=80fc00ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T11:22:45.000Z","msg":"can you see their eyes?"},{"pid":"4d6551bb82a40172166348642d0a8f056acce6de","tid":2164763,"uid":156